Name: Apple menu

Synonyms: Apple menu

Type: glossary

Description:
The leftmost <menu> in the <menu bar> on <Mac OS> and <OS X|OS X systems>. 
 
On <Mac OS|Mac OS systems>, the Apple menu contains the current application's About <menu item>.

